<plot>Pommetje Horlepiep is hired by Jonkeer Sebastiaan Roos van Leeuwenborgh to be his manservant and chauffeur. He is also tasked to accompany the nobleman whenever he performs a good deed to help the less fortunate members of society. When Sir Sebastian immigrates to Italy, his brother Theobald (nicknamed Baldi) takes up residence at the family mansion and picks up Sebastian's work.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?438251</url></doc>
